            <title>[LU-7349] New mount option to skip lfsck auto resuming when server mount</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7349</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sometime, the LFSCK may crash the system, and when the system mount up again, the unfinished LFSCK will be automatically resumed from the latest checkout, then the LFSCK may cause the system corruption again. Then the system drops into inaccessible status.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
